                            <comment id="12579159" author="ruwan" created="Sun, 16 Mar 2008 04:37:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have excluded this test case till we find a better approach&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12594010" author="veithen" created="Sat, 3 May 2008 16:55:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Running the test case now causes a javax.mail.AuthenticationFailedException. I checked the accounts and synapse.test.1 has been disabled.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12594030" author="veithen" created="Sat, 3 May 2008 21:00:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changed the unit tests to use mock JavaMail store and transport providers so that they no longer depend on GMail. This solves the issue, but still need to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;clean up (in particular remove duplicate code!!);&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
